template:
Dear {{employer_name}},

I hope this email finds you well. I'm reaching out regarding the {{job_title}} position you have open at {{company_name}}.

I'm pleased to present {{candidate_name}}, a candidate whose profile is an excellent match for your requirements. Here's a brief overview of their qualifications:

{{cv_summary}}

Key strengths that align with your requirements:
{{matching_skills}}

I believe {{candidate_name}} would be a valuable addition to your team based on their experience and skills. Their full profile and CV are attached to this email for your review.

If you would like to proceed with this candidate, please let me know, and I'll be happy to arrange an interview or provide any additional information you may need.

Best regards,
{{consultant_name}}
Recruitment Consultant
RecrutementPlus
Phone: {{consultant_phone}}

Dear {{candidate_name}},

Thank you for confirming your availability. This email is to confirm your interview for the {{job_title}} position at {{company_name}}.

Interview Details:
- Date: {{interview_date}}
- Time: {{interview_time}}
- Format: {{interview_format}}
- {{if_video_link}}Meeting Link: {{video_link}}{{/if_video_link}}
- {{if_location}}Location: {{interview_location}}{{/if_location}}

You will be meeting with:
{{interviewer_details}}

What to Prepare:
- Please review the job description thoroughly
- Be prepared to discuss your experience with {{key_skills_focus}}
- Consider preparing questions about the role and company
{{if_additional_instructions}}{{additional_instructions}}{{/if_additional_instructions}}

If you need to reschedule or have any questions before the interview, please don't hesitate to contact me.

Good luck with your interview! I look forward to hearing about how it goes.

Best regards,
{{consultant_name}}
Recruitment Consultant
RecrutementPlus
Phone: {{consultant_phone}}

Dear {{candidate_name}},

On behalf of {{company_name}}, I am delighted to formally offer you the position of {{job_title}}. Congratulations!

Following your successful interviews, the team at {{company_name}} was impressed with your experience, skills, and enthusiasm. They believe you would be an excellent addition to their organization.

Offer Details:
- Position: {{job_title}}
- Type: {{employment_type}}
- Start Date: {{start_date}}
- Salary: {{salary}}
- Benefits: {{benefits}}
- Work Location: {{work_location}}
- Reporting to: {{reporting_manager}}

The formal offer letter from {{company_name}} is attached to this email. It contains all the specific details of your employment offer and any additional information you may need.

To accept this offer, please sign the attached offer letter and return it to us by {{response_deadline}}.

If you have any questions about the offer or need any clarification, please don't hesitate to contact me.

Congratulations once again! We're thrilled for your success and have enjoyed working with you throughout this recruitment process.

Best regards,
{{consultant_name}}
Recruitment Consultant
RecrutementPlus
Phone: {{consultant_phone}}

Dear {{candidate_name}},

I hope this email finds you well. Based on your profile and preferences in our system, I'd like to bring your attention to a new job opportunity that matches your skills and career interests.

Job Details:
- Position: {{job_title}}
- Company: {{company_name}}
- Location: {{job_location}}
- Type: {{employment_type}}
- Key Requirements: {{key_requirements}}

Why This Job Might Interest You:
Based on your profile, you have {{matching_experience}} years of experience with {{matching_skills}}, which aligns perfectly with what {{company_name}} is looking for in their ideal candidate.

If you're interested in this opportunity, please reply to this email or click the button below to express your interest. I'd be happy to provide more details and discuss the next steps.

{{apply_button}}

If you're not interested in this specific opportunity but would like to continue receiving job matches, there's no need to take any action. We'll continue to notify you of relevant opportunities based on your profile.

Best regards,
{{consultant_name}}
Recruitment Consultant
RecrutementPlus
Phone: {{consultant_phone}}

Dear {{candidate_name}},

This is a friendly reminder that your interview for the {{job_title}} position at {{company_name}} is scheduled for tomorrow, {{interview_date}} at {{interview_time}}.

Interview Details:
- Format: {{interview_format}}
- {{if_video_link}}Meeting Link: {{video_link}}{{/if_video_link}}
- {{if_location}}Location: {{interview_location}}{{/if_location}}
- Duration: Approximately 45 minutes

Reminder of what to prepare:
- Review the job description and your application
- Be prepared to discuss your experience with {{key_skills_focus}}
- Have some questions ready about the role and company
- If it's a video interview, please test your equipment in advance

If you need to reschedule or have any last-minute questions, please contact me as soon as possible.

Good luck with your interview! I'm confident you will do well.

Best regards,
{{consultant_name}}
Recruitment Consultant
RecrutementPlus
Phone: {{consultant_phone}}
